ers?id=hgE-AAAAIBAJ&sjid=a0kMAAAAIBAJ&pg=1526%2C1187553 |title=Gallardo upstages Strange |newspaper=[[The Glasgow Herald]] |date=6 October 1981 |page=15}}</ref>\n*1981 [[Panama Open]]\n*1986 [[Fred Meyer Challenge]] (with [[Peter Jacobsen]]; Shared title with [[Greg Norman]] & [[Gary Player]])\n*1989 [[RMCC Invitational]] (with [[Mark O'Meara]]), [[PGA Grand Slam of Golf]] (unofficial event), [[Skins Game (PGA Tour)|Skins Game]]\n*1990 [[Skins Game (PGA Tour)|Skins Game]]\n\n==Major championships==\n===Wins (2)===\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n!Year!!Championship!!54 holes!!Winning score!!Margin!!Runner(s)-up\n|-style=\"background:#FBCEB1;\"\n|[[1988 U.S. Open (golf)|1988]] ||[[U.S. Open (golf)|U.S. Open]] ||1 shot lead ||\u22126 (70-67-69-72=278) ||Playoff<sup>1</sup> ||{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Nick Faldo]]\n|-style=\"background:#FBCEB1;\"\n|[[1989 U.S. Open (golf)|1989]] ||[[U.S. Open (golf)|U.S. Open]] <small> (2) ||3 shot deficit ||\u22122 (71-64-73-70=278) ||1 stroke ||{{flagicon|USA}} [[Chip Beck]], {{flagicon|USA}} [[Mark McCumber]], {{flagicon|WAL}} [[Ian Woosnam]]\n|}\n<sup>1</sup>Defeated Nick Faldo in an 18-hole playoff \u2013 Strange 71 (E), Faldo 75 (+4).\n\n===Results timeline===\n{| cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"1\" style=\"font-size: 95%; border: #aaa solid 1px; border-collapse: collapse;text-align:center;\"\n|- style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"\n!align=\"left\"|Tournament !! 1975 !! 1976 !! 1977 !! 1978 !! 1979 \n|-\n|align=left|[[Masters Tournament]]\n|CUT\n|T15 <span style=\"font-size:87%;\">LA</span>\n|CUT\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|-\n|align=left|[[U.S. Open (golf)|U.S. Open]]\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|CUT\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|-\n|align=left|[[The Open Championship]]\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|CUT\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|-\n|align=left